snippet.textDisplay: Dropped mandates, lotsa travel. Get the stimulus out now! Late but better than never! Inflation, war, this pandemic, soaring food and gas prices all hitting Americans at once! Let's get moving to help our own citizens! Crime and violence is ramping up all over. Not nearly enough mental health providers or police forces left to even start to keep people just safe. Sending out healing thoughts and good will to all!
